Post Caption:
Hypermedia as the Engine of Application State.
A truly RESTful API tells the client what it can do next.

Response:
{
  "id": 123,
  "status": "pending",
  "links": [
    { "rel": "cancel", "href": "/orders/123/cancel" }
  ]
}

The API guides the flow. The frontend doesn't need to guess the logic.
Rarely implemented, but powerful for decoupling.

#RESTAPI #WebArchitecture #HATEOAS #Backend #APIStandards
